overview: The rivalry between the manipulative boss of an advertising agency and her talented protégée escalates from stealing credit to public humiliation to murder.
tagline: No backstabbing. Just business

overview: A down-on-his luck businessman organizes an excursion to Sir Henry Morgan's Island for a treasure hunt only to encounter a mysterious phantom and murder.
A group of friends travel to a wilderness area to play a survival game. Soon they unexpectedly find themselves in a real-life survival situation.
tagline: Dawn Of A New Breed Of Heroes

overview: A Portuguese tuna fisherman (Edward G. Robinson) catches his bride (Zita Johann) with his first mate (Richard Arlen).
tagline: Jungle holds no terrors for these bloodthirsty white-belled cannibals!

overview: The Big Bad Wolf torments Robin Hood and the Three Little Pigs.
A robin is shot so the woodland community holds a trial to investigate in this Silly Symphony.
Two little pigs cry wolf on their brother and then an actual wolf comes.
The We and the I is the heartfelt and comical story of the final bus ride home for a group of young high school students and graduates.
A summer heat wave and a series of sexual encounters connect a group of New Yorkers.
A woman turns to prescription medication as a way of handling her anxiety concerning her husband's upcoming release from prison.
tagline: One pill can change your life.

overview: Interwoven stories of what it is to be a mom seen through the lens of photographer Rigby Gray.
An insane preacher seeks retribution from the local crime syndicate for the violent death of his family and the burning of his church in a horrendous ghetto crime spree.
tagline: It's judgement day.

overview: Former getaway driver Charlie Bronson jeopardizes his Witness Protection Plan identity in order to help his girlfriend get to Los Angeles. The feds and Charlie's former gang chase them on the road.
tagline: A Comedy That Never Takes Its Foot Off The Gas

overview: """Documentary examining what happens to some of the biggest names in the history of the adult entertainment industry after they leave the business and try and live """"normal"""" lives."""
tagline: Can they really live a normal life after porn?

overview: A demon is trapped in a monastery. 400 years later a young girl arrives at the monastery to study.
tagline: Dare you enter the labyrinth?

overview: Three suburban English families' lives intertwine with tragic consequences.

Computer genius and chess champion Ted Danson is lured into service by secret agent Eleanor Parker and becomes a reluctant hero thanks to a number of exploits with villainous Christopher Lee and his army of lethal blue-eyed blonde women.
A successful businessman attempting to resurrect his life buys and boards a dilapidated sailboat.

A love story centered on the lives of three young German soldiers in the years following World War I. Their close friendship is strengthened by their shared love for the same woman who is dying of tuberculosis.
tagline: .. Torn from a million souls!

overview: A medical examiner suspects a vampire might be responsible for the mysterious murders at the Sherwood School For Girls.
tagline: She Will GIVE YOU Nightmares...FOR EVER!

overview: Will Hay plays a bragging sea captain whose maritime experience actually extends to navigating a coal barge down inland waterways. His tall tales catch him out when he is co-erced into commanding an unseaworthy ship by an unscrupulous shipping agent who means to have it wrecked. This was the first film to couple Will Hay with both Moore Marriott and Graham Moffatt.
Four Sons is a 1940 film directed by Archie Mayo. It stars Don Ameche and Eugenie Leontovich. It is a remake of the 1928 film of the same name.
An engaged attorney and a divorcee fall for each other in 1870s Manhattan.
A detective investigates a series of murders that he begins to suspect are being committed by a woman involved in prostitution and narcotics trafficking.

Logan Cates (Rory Calhoun) sets out to rescue a white woman captured by Apache Indians and prevent a war. On the way he is joined by a few civilians and a small band of soldiers at a water hole. They are ambushed and laid siege to by Apache. As their food and water supplies dwindle a storm arrives which enables Cates to put an escape plan into action.
tagline: FLAMING ARROWS VS. HOME-MADE BOMBS

overview: A bizarre portrait of the New York singles scene.
A magnet moves on a floor. A moth beats against a window. A doll child watches the magnet; threads of metal filings gather around the magnet.
A reporter's (Johnny Downs) girlfriend's (Anne Nagel) father (George Zucco) injects a farmhand with wolf blood.
tagline: The blood of a wolf he placed in the veins of a man... and created a monster such as the world has never known!

overview: More hubub in the little town full of secrets when a visiting author trys to pry loose some juicy scandals!

Two lazy screenwriters need a story for the studio's cowboy star. A studio waitress turns out to be pregnant. This gives them the idea for a movie about a cowboy and a baby. The waitress's baby becomes the star. The cowboy and his agent run off with the waitress and her valuable asset. The writers retaliate by hiring an unemployed extra to impersonate the baby's father. But the extra already knows the waitress...
Long-time friends reconnect when one returns to their small Massachusetts town for a funeral.

originalTitle: Time Zero: The Last Year of Polaroid Film
overview: Documentary covering the end of an era as Polaroid stops producing its signature cameras and film as well as The Impossible Project to keep instant photography alive.
Follows the Boston Red Sox' Tim Wakefield and the New York Mets' R.A. Dickey - the only two major league pitchers who use the unpredictable knuckleball - during the 2011 season.
tagline: To gain power you must first give up control.

overview: """Dizzy society matron Emily Kilbourne has a habit of hiring ex-cons and hobos as servants. Her latest find is a handsome """"tramp"""" who shows up at her doorstep and soon ends up in a chauffeur's uniform. He also catches the eye of her pretty Geraldine."""
tagline: """IT TOPS """"TOPPER"""" BY A HUNDRED HOWLS!"""

overview: A modest country doctor in the antebellum South has to contend with his daughter's upcoming marriage and an affectionate medicine show elephant.
tagline: She Brought a New Kind of Love to the South!

originalTitle: Avatar: Creating the World of Pandora
overview: The Making-of James Cameron's Avatar. It shows interesting parts of the work on the set.
This tale of intrigue finds Valentina Cortese involved in an assassination plot. She helps the police apprehend the conspirators after an innocent bystander is accidentally killed.
tagline: LOOK OUT FOR THIS MAN! HE LIVES! AND LOVES! AND MURDERS!

overview: The story of a young pastor coming to a small town in the United States to set up his ministry.  The movie tells of the various relationships and struggles he goes through as he goes about raising his family and preaching to the community.
tagline: """""""Take Your Choice...Either I Speak...Or My Pistols Do!"""""""

overview: The ringmaster of a flea circus inherits a fortune...if he can find which chair it's hidden in.
tagline: Fred bagged the best for his merry 12 million dollar murder mystery!

overview: True story of boxers Joe Louis and Max Schmeling and their enduring friendship.
Flirtatious mermaid Miranda swaps places with a schoolteacher who has gone on holiday. All is well until she falls in love with a human.

originalTitle: The Happy Hooker Goes To Washington
overview: The world's most famous madame is called to Washington to testify before Congress.
tagline: She served her country... the only way she knew how!

overview: Husband-and-wife vaudeville stars separate when success goes to his head.
tagline: IT'S GOT EVERYTHING!

overview: A romantic comedy that brings together three disparate characters who are learning to face a challenging and often confusing world as they struggle together against a common demon: sex addiction.
tagline: Life is a journey you never have to take alone.

overview: A strict father loosens up enough to let his children take a day off school for a trip to the countryside. But things turn darker when the family realize he is planning to make it their last outing ever.
tagline: His job kept him sane! Now he's just lost it...

overview: """Hitchcock follows the relationship between director Alfred Hitchcock and his wife Alma Reville during the making of his most famous film """"Psycho"""" - and the trials and tribulations the director faced from Hollywood censors."""
tagline: Good evening.

overview: Scholiere Denise is ontevreden met haar leven en als ze de 19-jarige charmante Michael tegenkomt lijkt haar verlangen naar luxe en romantiek vervuld te worden. Maar Michael investeert in haar uit eigen belang.
A herpetologist investigating a series of fatal rattlesnake attacks discovers that the creatures have been infected by a mysterious nerve gas disposed of in the desert by the military.
tagline: What a horrible way to die! They're waiting to slither you!

overview: A small Army patrol unit and a couple of former Confederates reluctantly throw in their lot together after being attacked by a band of Native Americans.
tagline: Savage by savage...they fought out of a deadly Apache torture trap!

overview: Patty Sullivan (Erica Eleniak) is a battered woman who decides to take charge of her life by taking boxing lessons to better protect herself when her boyfriend becomes violent. Patty soon learns she has some talent for boxing and sets her sights on competing in a professional fight. More is on the line than just the woman's title.
tagline: She couldn't run from her past. So she fought for her future.

overview: A poor singer in a bar masquerades a rich society woman thanks to a rich benefactor.
A young woman learns of her adoption and eventually quits her law firm job and goes on a journey to find her birth mother.
Winning your childhood sweetheart can create more problems than it solves.
An alien is pursued as a traitor by his own race because he refuses to kill humans.
tagline: Marauding Wolf Raiders in Space Chase to the Death.

overview: Two highway road workers spend the summer of 1988 away from their city lives. The isolated landscape becomes a place of misadventure as the men find themselves at odds with each other and the women they left behind.

A bunch of pernicious salamander men from the planet Kulimon in the Moffit Galaxy plan on taking over Earth by unleashing a lethal plague on mankind. It's up to valiant superhero Starman from the Emerald Planet to save the human race before it's too late.

It's the height of the Cold War between the United States and the Soviet Union with the Communists launching a spy satellite that has the Free World leaders in a panic. Fears about the nature of the satellite force the United States to send an agent undercover behind the Iron Curtain to discover what the Soviets have learned. What he finds is the Communists have used the information acquired from their spy satellite to help them perfect a new and even more deadly nuclear weapon.
tagline: From Another Continent ... Destruction!!! Panic!! ... before the Rocket Strikes!

overview: Drug lords take over the empire left by convicted Sonny Hokori.
A street smart runner develops an intense rivalry with an equally ambitious wealthy young athlete.
The happy life of an Eskimo is disastrously changed when he mingles with an unscrupulous white trader.
A group of medical students undertake some silly and frightening endeavors in order to pledge a fraternity.
Hypochondriac Danny Weems gets drafted and accidentally smuggles his girlfriend aboard his Pacific-bound troopship.

The story of a murder trial where a Mexican boy is accused of the death of a Caucasian girl. The two-faced attorney (Arthur Kennedy) who takes the boy's case is only interested in defending him so he can exploit his Communist-backed organization for their own underhanded purposes. He and his organization bring in an idealistic law professor (Glenn Ford) who agrees to represent the boy in court.
tagline: Tense! Timely! Thrilling!

overview: A look at the mysterious relationship between Victorian art critic John Ruskin and his teenage bride Effie Gray.
tagline: The Celebrity Scandal of the Victorian era

overview: Naked Harbour is a movie about Finnish love in the year 2011. It is a story about people who seek love and acceptance at any cost. During one winter week all its characters face something irreversible.
tagline: Everybody wants to be touched

overview: """A young screenwriter allows others to exploit her in the hopes of """"making it"""" in Hollywood."""
tagline: From the sensual world of Harold Robbins comes the story of a woman's struggle for fame in Hollywood.

overview: Story of the American Prairie as it was when vast herds of bison and elk grazed.
tagline: A tribute to nature untouched by today.

overview: A group of coeds from a small conservative college break out of their shells when their marching band bus breaks down in Fort Lauderdale during Spring Break.
A gang of bank robbers team up with the residents of an old people's home to try to survive a zombie outbreak.
tagline: The undead are brown bread.

overview: Four couples meet for Sunday brunch only to discover they are stuck in a house together as the world may be about to end.
tagline: Are You Prepared?

overview: Story of three buddies at the Virginia Military Institute. Cadet Bing Edwards is secretly married and soon to be a father.

Former buffalo hunter and entrepreneur Wyatt Earp arrives in the lawless cattle town of Wichita Kansas. His skill as a gun-fighter make him a perfect candidate for Marshal but he refuses the job until he feels morally obligated to bring law and order to this wild town.
tagline: THE TRUE SAVAGE STORY OF WYATT EARP!

overview: A glowing brain-like creature arrives on a beach near a rocket test site via a teleportation beam. The alien communicates telepathically with the children of scientists. The kids start doing the alien's bidding as the adults try to find out what's happening to their unruly offspring.

A hybrid creature - half piranha and half anaconda -- attacks a low-budget horror movie crew on location near her nest when her egg is stolen. Now they must outrun and kill the deadly piranhaconda as well as stop the mad scientist who stole the egg - before they all become dinner.
tagline: Part Snake! Part Fish! All Killer!

originalTitle: My Father And The Man In Black
overview: The story of promoter Saul Holiff's turbulent life and his success making Johnny Cash a superstar.
Two high school students become stranded on a tropical island and must rely on each other for survival. They learn more about themselves and each other while falling in love.
tagline: The Awakening

overview: French pirate Jean Lafitte rescues a girl and joins the War of 1812.
tagline: The greatest adventure romance in Cecil B De Mille's glorious gallery of screen triumphs!

overview: Based on Graham Greene's novel about a flawed but devoted priest in 1930s Mexico who attempts to perform his duties while eluding a police lieutenant determined to capture him.
tagline: Out of Graham Greene's novel that made the world gasp--the drama of a priest who somehow stumbled onto the road to martyrdom

overview: A film featuring performances of several stars of the Latin Jazz music scene.
"""Spanish version of  Henry James' classic tale """"Turn of the Screw""""."""
A day in the life of a Chicago cab driver is examined as he picks up fares from the good and bad parts of the city and emotionally connects to many of his passengers.
tagline: Do you dare pay the fare?

overview: """Idiosyncratic new recruit Francis """"Ike"""" Farrell tries to help the Cubs to the pennant with his pitching and hitting."""
tagline: The man with a million excuses!

overview: A plane crash-lands on a jungle island inhabited by a scientist and his nubile young daughters. Complications ensue.
tagline: A Secret Eden Turned into a Raging Hell!

overview: A western set on the New Mexico frontier a few years after the Civil War and centered on a struggling young family and the mining company who wants to buy their land.
Alan Zweig analyzes the phenomenon of record collecting through himself and others.
tagline: A Camera. A Collection. An Obsession.

overview: A teenager finds herself transported to a deep forest setting where a battle between the forces of good and the forces of evil is taking place. She bands together with a rag-tag group characters in order to save their world -- and ours.
tagline: Discover a world beyond your imagination

overview: Two recently laid-off men in their 40s try to make it as interns at a successful Internet company where their managers are in their 20s.
tagline: Hiring them was a brilliant mistake.

overview: Armand and Marie survive in the streets until a scientist takes them in after a botched robbery.
The sons of a disgraced British officer try to clear his name.
A group of volunteers find themselves fighting for their lives when a drug trial goes horribly wrong.
tagline: One new drug. Seven volunteers. Seventeen hours of hell.

overview: Just a Little Harmless Sex examines a young married couple that faces a serious break-up when the husband is caught committing adultery with a prostitute.
Documentary about the quest for peace between rival gangs in Birmingham.
Manoel de Oliveira's autobiographical documentary about returning to his hometown.
Fortune hunters from all over the country rush to the Klondike in 1897 to seek their fortunes in the gold are tested by hardships of the journey.
A man is hired to run a bank which turns out to be a sperm bank.
1970's pop culture icons Danny Bonaduce and Barry Williams face off in the hunt for the legendary mountain creature.
A group of six ex-high school cheerleaders are stalked by a killer with a medieval war hammer and battle axe during their first Spring Break from college.
A European immigrant becomes a master of industry but almost loses his family.
tagline: OUT OF THE HOPE AND COURAGE OF A MAN ...THE LOVE AND DEVOTION OF A WOMAN!

overview: A Chinese wife returns to the American family she left and moves in on her daughter's (Lupe Velez) beau (Lloyd Hughes).
A woman infiltrates a criminal mob to avenge her brother's death.
tagline: WIDOW STEALS GANGSTERS LOVE

overview: A plain-Jane stenographer blossoms when she accompanies her boss on a business trip to Paris.
Women around the globe begin disappearing when a renegade race of top-heavy aliens from the planet Angvia begin snatching them off the streets.
"""Follow-up to Andy Griffith's big hit in """"No Time for Sergeants"""" moves the action to the Coast Guard and WW II."""
tagline: The Ship's Cook who has the Coast Guard in a Stew!

overview: The cavalry defend a small town from indians.
A smooth-talking French thief (George Sanders) wangles his way into an important position as prefect of police.
tagline: Every man has his price... and every woman pays it.

originalTitle: The Private Affairs of Bel Ami
overview: A self-serving journalist (George Sanders) uses influential women in late-1800s Paris and denies the one (Angela Lansbury) who truly loves him.
tagline: All women take to men who have the appearance of wickedness

overview: An ex-football brute (Anthony Quinn) and his beatnik gang take a rich girl (Carol Ohmart) and her boyfriend hostage (Arthur Franz) at a jazz joint.
tagline: This is a New Motion Picture as Daring as the Screen Will Ever Get!

overview: Martians replace scientist & his family to pave way for invasion.
tagline: Strange Invisible Astro-Energy Unleashed Leaves Mankind A Human Shell As It Destroys His Body And Brain!

overview: An elite hitman returns to erase his past only to find that somebody has messed with his future.
A young hustler tries to get drug money by selling a boy to a middle-aged man; his plans are disrupted when the kid dies.
Romeo and Juliet story set amidst horseracing in Kentucky. The family feud of lovers Jack and Sally goes back to the Civil War and is kept alive by her Uncle Peter.

An east coast efficiency expert who stakes his reputation on his ability to turn around a financially troubled Hollywood studio receives some help from a former child star who now works as a stand-in for the studio.
tagline: Hail! The conquering hero comes!

overview: A pair of young ladies cause trouble at the cinema with their lavish hats.
Murders result from an uncle's wish to eliminate beneficiaries to a will.
tagline: IT'S MURDER!...and it's HORRIFIC!

overview: A freak tsunami traps shoppers at a coastal Australian supermarket inside the building ... along with a 12-foot great white shark.
tagline: Cleanup on aisle 7.

overview: A gangster (Alan Ladd) escapes from boot camp with a canteen girl (Helen Walker) and finds his gang's new boss (Sheldon Leonard) helping Nazi spies.
A female police detective investigates a series of serial murders while dealing with sexist hostility from her male comrades.
A policeman in New Mexico takes payoff money but still manages to go after a racketeer.
tagline: Meet the brother with a badge... on the take!

overview: Super Crazy is the first feature length special from New York City's Todd Barry.
June and her friends take over a service station formerly run by her uncle. They perform every trick in the book to attract the customers.
tagline: """They give new meaning to the term """"full-service station""""!"""

overview: This horror film revolves around a sinister vampire (John Carradine) who sends out a horde of undead beauties to bring back victims for his dinner.
tagline: Warm Blood Isn't All They Suck!

overview: A Peruvian schoolteacher conspires with a journalist to assassinate the official responsible for her fiancé's murder.
Two aging comedians who acrimoniously dissolved their act eight years earlier must overcome their differences when they have the chance for a lucrative movie comeback.
Found footage of an expedition into the Congo jungle where a team of explorers stumbles upon a colony of Dinosaurs.
tagline: The discovery of a lifetime will become a fight for survival.

originalTitle: An American Girl: McKenna Shoots for the Stars
overview: A young girl (Jade Pettyjohn) struggles to maintain her school grades while competing as a gymnast.
Romantic comedy adapted from a Somerset Maugham play.
tagline: JUST MARRIED.......BUT TO WHOM?

overview: A young playboy who learns he has one month until he becomes infertile sets out to procreate as much as possible.
tagline: He never wanted to have kids until life kicked him where it counts

overview: Three years after his divorce from his model-wife is the psychologist Larry Livingstone ready for a new commitment. He falls in love with the young widow Beth who has two children. But Beth and the children are still in mourning over their dead husband and father and Larry finds it a bit difficult to penetrate their reservations. Larry himself has to deal with his ex-wife and his love for his own two kids. Slowly both Beth and the children realise that they have to go on with their lives and that they have been giving a second chance.
tagline: Just when you thought it couldn't happen again.

overview: A woman's husband is murdered and she and her lover must find the killer or stand accused of doing it themselves.
tagline: Is this any way to begin a love affair?

overview: Silent comedy. A deja vu story of runaway young love.
The action takes place during the Great War in the home of the First Lord of the Admiralty.
A dynamic duo in silk and ermine entertain hick businessmen looking for a good time while in Manhattan.
Chorus girl Eadie is determined to marry a millionaire without sacrificing her virtue.
Young free-thinkers turn conventionally jealous when they marry.
Slackers who live for free in a rock star's mansion find that their ride on the gravy train is coming to an end with the sale of their pal's residence.
tagline: Living on easy street just got a little harder.

overview: A dancer who has just gotten engaged to her partner and choreographer and is about to embark on a major career is devastated to learn that she has contracted polio.
A British colonel (Ray Milland) escapes from the Gestapo to the Black Forest and poses as a Gypsy's (Marlene Dietrich) mate.
tagline: Strange . . . Amazing . . . Their Love Story !

overview: A disturbing portrait of contemporary youth culture where the lines between reality and fiction are blurred with often frightening results.

A Canadian-Brith film adaptation of Salman Rushdie's novel of the same name. The film tells the story of a pair of children born within moments of India gaining independence from England grow up in the country that is nothing like their parent's generation.

originalTitle: The Biggest Bundle of Them All
overview: A kidnapped mobster (Vittorio De Sica) persuades his captors to help him rob platinum ingots from a train.
tagline: This is the world's sexiest robbery!

overview: Sierra Nevada Jones must fight a villainous rancher to regain the land that is rightfully hers.
tagline: She strips off her petticoats . . . and straps on her guns !

overview: An Arab surgeon living in Tel Aviv discovers a dark secret about his wife in the aftermath of a suicide bombing.
An island fugitive (Humphrey Bogart) and his bride (Margaret Lindsay) make room for a shipwrecked detective (Donald Woods).
The plot revolves around the return of a Spanish princess from America to her native country Spain. To help her she enlists the aid of a reluctant hero (Tony Anthony).
tagline: Hung by his heels...Barbecued...Shot with a cannon.  Now it's his turn to get mean!

overview: Justice needs to be served at Britain's most notorious young offenders institute.
tagline: This summer ... justice will be served

overview: A Bajau midwife copes with the irony of her own infertility amid the deprivations of her gypsy community in Tawi-Tawi. A saga of island life stuck between the devil of passion and the deep blue sea of tradition.
An American (Lloyd Bridges) returns to his London lover (Moira Lister) and joins the search for a limping sniper.
Three unique horror stories connected by a bookend story tells of the horrifying past a young couples potential dream house has endured.
tagline: Every house has a past

overview: A gang of ruthless highway killers kidnap a wealthy couple traveling cross country only to shockingly discover that things are not what they seem.
tagline: No one runs. No one escapes.

overview: """Self-proclaimed """"D-Lister"""" and two-time Emmy Award-winning comedian Kathy Griffin's latest comedy specials take you on a wild ride behind the scenes of Hollywood's most salacious celebrity gossip."""
Tongues begin to wag when a lonely widow becomes romantically involved with a military man. Problems arise when the gossip is filtered down to her own children.
tagline: Of all the dramatic triumphs from Warners this one is the greatest!

overview: A short futuristic film featuring Augmented reality and Gamification by Eran May-raz and Daniel Lazo. This is our graduation project from Bezaleal academy of arts.
tagline: Sight

overview: A group of US Navy weathermen taking measurements in the Gobi desert in World War II are forced to seek the help of Mongol nomads to regain their ship while under attack from the Japanese.
tagline: ADVENTURE AS FIERY AND FURIOUS AS THE FLAMING SANDS OF CHINA'S GOBI DESERT!

overview: Backwater is doomed by the regular visits of the undertaker and its dwellers blame a tramp.
A young woman moves with her mother to her mother's hometown and is haunted by the ghost of a dead teenager.

A woman tormented by ghostly apparitions and a professor of psychic phenomena investigate other-worldly disturbances and unlock the secret of a malevolent force reaching out for vengeance from beyond the grave.
tagline: It's going to be a hell of a night!

overview: The president (Bob Newhart) and his boozing wife (Madeline Kahn) go to Africa to bargain for their abducted daughter's (Gilda Radner) return.
A strange creature races against time to make the most important and beautiful creation of his life.
tagline: Life is what you make it.

overview: A modern priest investigates nuns' claims that the Devil is present in their nunnery.
tagline: Say Your Prayers

overview: Pat Garrett arrives in Abilene where he catches five of Butch Cassidy's gang. He calls in Wyatt Earp and Bat Masterson and they learn there is a half million dollar shipment of money arriving by train and Cassidy is amassing enough men to take it.
tagline: Warner's Big Six-Gun Saga!

overview: A group of friends who venture into the remote Texas woods for a party weekend find themselves stalked by Bigfoot.
tagline: The legend is real. So is the terror.

overview: A teenage girl comes to terms with the unexplained death of the boy next door.
Secret agent Julie Cosgrove is walking into her most dangerous mission yet.
A young working-class girl causes a stir when she sneaks off for a romantic getaway with the wealthy heir of the mill where she works.
Jimmy needs $900 to clear a gambling debt but a series of lies leads to Ray trying to raise the cash from friend's who owe him money.
tagline: A romantic comedy for the romantically challenged.

overview: An undercover police officer must prove that a lonely man's missing wife was murdered.
A footman seduces a count's daughter. Adaptation of August Strindberg's famous play.
tagline: Worlds apart... bound by desire.

overview: Grace tries to be the perfect mother and TV producer but finds trouble in juggling both.
tagline: A story about getting everything you want and what comes next

overview: A mysterious creature is killing a farmer's livestock.
An auto engineer (Herbert Marshall) and a professor's daughter (Jean Arthur) pose as married servants in a mobster's (Leo Carrillo) mansion.
tagline: SHE GAVE UP HER PARK BENCH FOR HIM! HE GAVE UP MILLIONS FOR HER!

overview: Paris 2002. Yellow cats appear on the walls. Chris Marker is looking for these mysterious cats and captures with his camera the political and international events of these last two years (war in Iraq...).
Two young couples backpacking through Ireland discover that one of Ireland's most famous legends is a terrifying reality.
tagline: A horror icon is reborn

overview: A young med student struggling with her tuition fees is drawn into the shady world of underground body modification.
tagline: Appearances are everything

overview: A 20-year-old homeless girl is suffering from post traumatic stress syndrome on the streets of Hollywood and Venice beach.

A meeting with a struggling actress (Niharika Singh) gives a mild-mannered filmmaker (Nawazuddin Siddiqui) the idea to break away from his controlling brother (Anil George) and direct a feature of his own.
A Texan arrives in Oregon and seeks justice for his innocently-hanged brother
tagline: A savage land beyond the law!

overview: It's 1875 and a young street urchin wants to see Queen Victoria...
tagline: At last it's here!

overview: A dramatization of the famous 1893 Massachusetts trial of the woman accused of murdering her father and stepmother with an ax.
Superman comes to Earth as a child and grows up to be his home's first superhero with his first major challenge being to oppose The Spider Lady.
US art dealer returns to his native Germany for a visit and is attracted by Nazi propaganda.
tagline: It Startled Millions! NOW...It Becomes the Great Screen Drama of Our Time!

overview: A propaganda film made during the Spanish Civil War in support of the Republican government against the rebellion by Gen. Francisco Franco's forces who were backed by Nazi Germany and Fascist Italy.  The film would have been seen by those making it as a documentary.

originalTitle: I Can Make You Love Me
overview: Laura Black has got it. She has got her master in computer science and she has got that great job in Silicon Valley. Time to say 'bye bye' to mom and dad and to leave Virginia. Everything seems to be fine with one exception. That guy Richard Farley at her new job. If he would stop his attempts to date her. Since weeks his psycho terror is going on now. Laura decides not to let him win. She does not want to be his 'victim'. May be an official complaint about Farley would solve her problem? Written by Oliver Heidelbach
tagline: Even the most innocent relationship can become a fatal attraction.

overview: A Cinderella story of a young country girl who comes to Hollywood and achieves movie stardom with the help of a publicity man.
tagline: Hal Roach's Musical Comedy!

overview: Explores our perception of time.
Dory is reunited with her friends Nemo and Marlin in the search for answers about her past. What can she remember? Who are her parents? And where did she learn to speak Whale?
tagline: An unforgettable journey she probably won't remember.

overview: A skeleton dances.

Former football player and wrestler Chris Nowinski's quest to publicize recent findings about the often dire consequences of head concussions sustained by athletes in contact sports ??injuries that have previously been considered momentary setbacks and ignored in the name of toughness and dedication to the team.
tagline: How much are you willing to lose for a game?

overview: """A victim from World War II's """"Death Railway"""" sets out to find those responsible for his torture. A true story."""
tagline: Revenge is never a straight line.

overview: Country boy joins a circus in the 1840s and falls in love with the bare-back rider. Later he falls in love with another circus runaway.
